name: Meetup Media
overview:
MeetupMedia is a mobile app start up located in Palo Alto, CA

Meetup Media operates an academic group Q&A App in the itunes store. Meetup Media is focused on creating Group Sharing Q&A Mobile Apps and experiences that make it easy to create groups large or small and generate on demand answers from college students and educators. Users can create or join a group community where they can ask or answer any number of relevant, user generated questions that their study groups are posting. By asking and receiving answers from groups of people users know, they are exchanging valuable information from a community they know and trust.
